Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:45.69,tab,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(324,96)}YUUKO! ZLIKVIDUJEM
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:50.71,tab,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(337,131)\fs28}Tomuto dievčaťu skutočne vadí strašidelný príbeh o Yuuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:53.96,tab,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(337,131)\fs28}Zaujímalo by nás, že či je to kvôli tomu, že sa tiež voláš Yuuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:55.70,tab,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\pos(520,377)}Vôbec nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:57.17,tab,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(337,131)\fs28}Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:59.20,tab,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29\pos(259,337)}Povedela som,\N že nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:00.05,tab,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\pos(248,349)}Strašidelný príbeh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:00.88,tab,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\pos(272,344)}Yuuko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:03.38,tab,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(337,131)\fs28}To ste vážne takí sprostí?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:04.14,tab,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(337,131)\fs28}Nevravte mi, že všetkému...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:05.34,tab,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(337,131)\fs28}... tomuto veríte!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.59,0:12:07.51,tab,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(337,131)\fs28}M-Máš pravdu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:09.81,tab,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(337,131)\fs28}Skutoční duchovia predsa nemôžu existovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:14.06,tab,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(337,131)\fs28}Avšak, \Nnepomôžete si, ak dostanete strach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.06,0:12:16.94,tab,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(337,131)\fs28}Všetci sa na tom zhodli.
