Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:42.80,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Zlikvidujem...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:46.49,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,... strašidelné príbehy a aj tých, ktorí im veria...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:49.69,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetkých, všetkých a všetko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.42,0:12:51.37,tab2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(322,201)}Yuuko
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:51.37,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:54.38,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,To ste vy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:57.42,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko! Čo máme urobiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:12:58.06,tab2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(318,304)}Yuuko
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:13:00.12,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Nedokázali sme nájsť Yuuko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.12,0:13:02.77,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Príde nás Akahito-san zabiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:08.49,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, jedinú koho Akahito-san zabije, je Yuuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:09.99,tab2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(318,304)}Yuuko-san
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:09.99,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:11.65,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.73,0:13:15.17,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Kvôli tomu Akahito-san hľadá Yuuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:17.37,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Obeťou má byť, Yuuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:25.59,tab2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,995)\pos(313,180)}Yuuko-san
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:21.02,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Akahito-san zabije Yuuko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:23.77,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Obeťou bude, Yuuko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:25.01,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Presne tak...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.10,0:13:27.84,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Akahito-san zabije Yuuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.27,0:13:31.25,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak Yuuko-san zomrie, my budeme...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:32.73,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,To je v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.28,0:13:36.89,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj keby sa čokoľvek stalo, ochránim vás za každú cenu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:39.78,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujeme, Yuuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:42.83,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Vlastne, Yuuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:49.60,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,"Zlikvidujem strašidelné príbehy"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:52.85,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslíš si, že je to naozaj možné?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:54.33,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Kto vie...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:14:00.98,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak by sa rozchýrilo, že Yuuko-san bola zabitá Akahitou-san, tak by to mohlo byť možné, nie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:02.31,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,To snáď nie...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.51,0:14:04.30,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san a tebe to nevadí?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:11.36,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Či vadí, alebo nevadí, nemám žiadne právo, to dievča zastaviť, ak je to to, čo chce ona.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:16.25,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Kvôli mojej existencii, je k tomuto donútená.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:19.14,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Je iba prirodzené, že ma nenávidí.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:22.20,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale, toto je kruté.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:25.15,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san, nie je to pre teba bolestivé?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:27.40,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Bolestivé?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:28.39,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:30.68,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Niiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:32.30,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirie-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:33.54,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,To je zlé!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.65,0:14:36.20,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirishima Yuuko bola vybraná, ako obeť pre Akahitu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.95,0:14:38.40,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo tým chceš povedať?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:41.35,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Veď predsa, za prípadom Akahity-san bola Kirishima-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:44.94,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Tie decká vzali príbeh veľmi vážne\N a zbláznili sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:46.56,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Nedá sa povedať, čo urobia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:50.54,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Poďme, Yuuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:52.27,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,So mnou?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:56.17,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale, ona to urobila preto, lebo ma nenávidí...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:57.23,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale aj tak!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:15:01.70,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale aj tak musíme byť tými, kto Kirishimu-san za každú cenu zachráni!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.80,0:15:17.26,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Mýlite sa! Ja nie som Yuuko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:18.74,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja nie som obeť!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:20.22,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Vďaka bohu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.22,0:15:22.16,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz už neumrieme.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.29,0:15:25.29,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Akahito-san nám už teraz odpustí.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.53,0:15:26.51,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Jasné...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:29.06,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretože sa zdá, že si to nikto z vás neuvedomil, tak vám to poviem...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:31.19,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Za príbehom Akahity-san, som bola ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:34.07,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetko toto som si vymyslela, takže...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:35.80,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, počúvate ma?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:39.98,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Vypočujte ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.56,0:15:44.01,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím vás, počúvajte.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:47.91,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Vypočujte ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:53.90,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Kto je do frrasa Yuuko-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:55.75,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Kto je do frasa Akahito-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:16:01.33,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Decká, musíte byť naozaj veľmi sprosté, ak sa bojíte vecí, ktoré nemôžu existovať a nedokážete sa od toho oslobodiť!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:04.72,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Existujú.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.49,0:16:07.29,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Akahito-san existuje.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:09.31,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Presne tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:12.93,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Veď presa všetci sme tak hrozne vystrašení.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:15.17,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Preto Yuuko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:17.20,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,... musíme obetovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:22.84,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Stačí Yuuko-san obetovať...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.99,0:16:24.98,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,... a už nikto nebude napadnutý.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:27.47,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Už sa nebudeme musieť báť.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.57,0:16:28.80,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo znamená obetovať?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:31.05,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Akahito-san chce Yuukinu-san krv.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:31.81,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuukinu-san krv?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.81,0:16:33.45,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Sfarbíme ju do červena.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:34.86,TOA06it,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak jej obetujeme Yuuko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:35.57,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Akahito-san nám odpustí.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:36.64,TOA06it,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san nás zachráni.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.90,0:16:37.89,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto znamená obetovať sa, všakže?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.12,0:16:39.39,TOA06it,,0000,0000,0000,,Kvôli tomu Yuuko-san existuje.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:40.32,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san nás všetkých zachráni.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.87,0:16:41.77,TOA06it,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikto z nás nechce umrieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:42.47,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Som na smrť vystrašený.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:44.13,TOA06it,,0000,0000,0000,,Nechcem umrieť... Nechcem umrieť...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:44.77,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Jediné čo potrebujeme, je obetovať Yuukinu-san krv...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.13,0:16:45.73,TOA06it,,0000,0000,0000,,Jediné čo musíme urobiť, je obetovať Yuuko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:46.34,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Konečne budeme môcť kľudne spať.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:47.73,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Konečne sa dokážem sústrediť na učenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:48.42,TOA06it,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď sa mi uľavilo, tak som vyhladol.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:49.33,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to len vďaka Yuuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:50.35,TOA06it,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretože Yuuko-san obetuje svoju krv.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.81,0:16:53.45,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Neopustila by si nás, všakže?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:52.14,TOA06it,,0000,0000,0000,,Zachráň ma, Yuuko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:55.15,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Veríme v teba, Yuuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:55.94,TOA06it,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san si jedinečná.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:57.02,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san je vyvolená Akahitou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:16:58.15,TOA06it,,0000,0000,0000,,Preto hľadala Yuuku-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:16:58.91,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím, vykrvácaj, Yuuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.15,0:16:59.71,TOA06it,,0000,0000,0000,,Akahito-san čoskoro dorazí.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.09,0:17:00.65,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san sa zmení zo strašidelného príbehu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.71,0:17:00.65,TOA06it,,0000,0000,0000,,... na legendu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:02.41,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Musíš byť veľmi šťastná, že môžeš všetkých zachrániť.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.71,0:17:03.42,TOA06it,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san nás všetkých zachráni?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:04.46,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san, si úžasná.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:06.19,TOA06it,,0000,0000,0000,,Už si pripravená, Yuuko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:07.36,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Poponáhľajte sa a obetujte Yuukinu-san krv.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:08.53,TOA06it,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím ťa, vykrvácaj, Yuuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.53,0:17:11.62,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak to urobíš, budeme môcť byť všetci šťastní!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:15.36,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujeme...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:15.12,yuuko2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(325,208)}Ďakujeme
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:16.57,yuuko2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(339,133)}Yuuko-san
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:16.57,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,... Yuuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.97,0:17:32.42,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,To je Akahito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.05,0:18:06.87,tab,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\c&H030300&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(319,47)}Ty nie si Yuuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:06.89,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty nie si Yuuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:09.51,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.83,0:18:13.84,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Táto tu nie je Yuuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:19.00,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Podvod je veľmi vážny prečin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:21.63,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Zaplatíte svojou krvou.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:36.92,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Zomrieme!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.21,0:18:39.28,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Zachráňte ma niekto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.28,0:18:42.16,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Nechcem umrieť!\N Nechcem umrieť!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.56,0:19:00.24,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie si zranená?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:02.84,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty si...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.96,0:19:07.99,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Pred chvíľou som videla...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:09.19,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,To bola...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:11.32,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,To bol...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.07,0:19:15.25,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,... duch zo starej školy, Yuuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:26.00,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Pomôžte mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:27.77,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Niekto...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:20:00.71,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Nebojíš sa strašidelných príbehov?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.46,0:20:03.68,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, vôbec sa ich nebojím.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:08.18,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Počuj...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:12.27,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirishima-san, z tvojho pohľadu, Yuuko-san stelesňuje všetko čo nenávidíš.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:16.20,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale skutočná Yuuko-san nie je desivý duch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.33,0:20:17.21,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Naozaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.83,0:20:19.76,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Pravdepodobne máš pravdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.60,0:20:24.85,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem tým iba povedať...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.90,0:20:29.27,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,... že ma aspoň nebudeš volať Yuuko-san, všakže?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:41.01,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:53.76,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.04,0:21:02.10,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Ehm, Yuuko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.86,0:21:05.21,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Deje sa niečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:07.88,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Odpusť mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:10.33,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,To čo som predtým povedal, nebolo správne.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.57,0:21:12.70,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:14.04,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,... bola som šťastná.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:24.78,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Teiichi-kun, pretože kvôli tomu čo hovoríš, som...
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.11,0:21:45.81,ED sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}Osamelosť pochádzajúca zo samoty
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.50,0:21:50.18,ED sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}Dávno vyblednutý úsmev
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.97,0:21:54.55,ED sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}Čo si ukrýval si mi dal
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.35,0:21:58.51,ED sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}všetko je mi drahé
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.85,0:22:04.04,ED sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}I keď stojíš pri mne
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.04,0:22:08.06,ED sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}Nedotýkaš sa ma
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.52,0:22:12.52,ED sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}Moje srdce, je ako mesiac
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.52,0:22:17.15,ED sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}Neustále sa mení
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.15,0:22:21.04,ED sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}Aj nesplnené sľuby
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.67,0:22:25.36,ED sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}Aj neusušené slzy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.06,0:22:29.67,ED sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}Nechám si všetko čo si mi dal
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.47,0:22:36.30,ED sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}V objatí tanca
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.11,0:21:45.88,ED jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}hitorikiri no sabishisa
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.52,0:21:50.36,ED jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}hitotoki no hohoemi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.05,0:21:54.63,ED jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}anata ga kureru mono wa
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.43,0:21:58.59,ED jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}minna itoshii
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.93,0:22:04.12,ED jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}sugu soko ni ite mo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.12,0:22:08.14,ED jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}furerarenai mono
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.60,0:22:12.60,ED jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}kokoro wa tsuki no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:17.23,ED jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}katachi wo kaeteku no
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.23,0:22:21.12,ED jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}kanawanai yakusoku mo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.75,0:22:25.44,ED jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}kawakanai namida mo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.14,0:22:29.75,ED jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}anata ga kureta mono wa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.55,0:22:36.38,ED jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}dakishimete odoru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.99,0:23:03.92,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Počuj, Kirie-san, prečo si ma vlastne zavolala kvôli tejto veci?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.97,0:23:06.52,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm? Myslím, že to bola trochu dobrá taktika na vystrašenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.52,0:23:10.03,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo? To mi chceš povedať, že to bol iba žart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.42,0:23:12.36,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Vlastne to ani nebol žart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.49,0:23:14.11,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,To je veľmi zlé!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.11,0:23:16.40,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Musíme sa odtiaľto dostať, lebo nás tu objaví učiteľ!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.40,0:23:18.67,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirie-san, rýchlo...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.86,0:23:22.14,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Do frasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.28,0:23:38.68,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyryté meno, je mojim symbolom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.18,0:23:41.94,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,To čo môžem vidieť, je moja pravda.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.39,0:23:44.17,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem zabudnúť, chcem zabudnúť.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.86,0:23:46.11,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Plač zo strachu.
