Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.53,0:23:47.72,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Siedma Záhada
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.72,0:23:49.27,TOA06,,0000,0000,0000,,Dievčina Zabudnutia.
